{
  "texts": [
    "Eqs (13) and (14) are used to derive the VGG19 and HOG features.",
    "Eq 15 is a notation for the process of combining the features that were extracted into a single vector.",
    "The proposed approach uses a feature fusion that relies on entropy, which works with an attached direction with 1 × 1186 dimensions [66].",
    "The feature vector has been given entropy to select the ideal characteristics according to score values.",
    "Both (16) and (17) are equations that characterize the features of probability, and (16) and (17) describe entropy."
  ]
}